Package: trendr
Title: A locally-linear state-space model (LLM-SSM) for calculating trend and rate of change of the trend from time series data.
Version: 1.0.0
Description: A locally-linear state-space model (LLM-SSM) for calculating trend and rate of change of the trend from time series data. Uses a Diffuse Kalman Filter (de Jong, Piet. 1991. doi:10.1214/aos/1176348139).
